Once you are banned, you will not be able to recover your account. You can only use another account to avoid being banned again. Also, after being banned, when you log into the game and see the ban screen, repeat the process and never enter the game where you were banned again to prevent it from happening again.

Steps to Follow
1️⃣ (Optional) First, log out / sign out of all your accounts ROBLOX (Microsoft Store, web, etc. ONLY ROBLOX) and make sure Roblox is completely closed.

2️⃣ On the Windows search bar, type "Disk Cleanup", select everything, clean bla bla bla, ok, select everything again and press ok to start the process.

